race.comment: HULKAMANIA (1) came back in fine fashion with a solid win at the Gold Coast and winning rider Youngberry sticks in the stirrups. Again gets the benefit of her 3kg claim and can go back-to-back to start the campaign. LIBERTY STEPS (4) has placed two from two around this circuit and will be rock-hard fit for this. Cannot be discounted lightly. The well-related PASIMA (7) (half to G3 winner and G2 placed Inkaruna) has placed two of three over this track and trip. Mixed his form last campaign however a third at this course, class and distance shows what he can do. AROUND THE BUOY (8) is a stayer resuming who should be hitting the line with gusto.
